	(text_box "Unused SPI signals: SPI2 (Need more info on jetson nano connections)\n\nAlso need confirmations on TBD pins and if they will be used\n\nAlso it would be nice to defin +3v3, +5V, +12V as global labels\n\nAlso need to add DIP pin settings for the AMT102-V encoders\n\nAlso it would be nice to add comments on where USB is routed maybe? I think thats extraneous to the schematic\n"
